				                <div>&lt;div style=&quot;background-color: #FFF; padding-left: 10px;&quot;&gt;Hello Richard,<br />
<br />
Sorry for the confusion, your WordPress admin area should still be accessible after you installed the HC Custom WP-Admin URL plugin. You just need use the &lt;strong&gt;WP-admin slug&lt;/strong&gt; that you set from step #8.<br />
<br />
